","line":427,"embedded":true},{"title":"bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_11_229_231_234_255_0.jpg","target":"images/bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_11_229_231_234_255_0.jpg","line":443,"embedded":true},{"title":"bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_11_136_600_363_308_0.jpg","target":"images/bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_11_136_600_363_308_0.jpg","line":447,"embedded":true},{"title":"bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_12_1127_223_399_278_0.jpg","target":"images/bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_12_1127_223_399_278_0.jpg","line":471,"embedded":true},{"title":"bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_12_1142_624_318_243_0.jpg","target":"images/bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_12_1142_624_318_243_0.jpg","line":485,"embedded":true},{"title":"bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_14_1141_1262_316_230_0.jpg","target":"images/bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_14_1141_1262_316_230_0.jpg","line":641,"embedded":true},{"title":"bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_21_216_1019_262_255_0.jpg","target":"images/bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_21_216_1019_262_255_0.jpg","line":897,"embedded":true},{"title":"cos $\\left( {\\pi  + \\alpha }\\right)  + \\mathrm{i}$ sin $\\left( {\\pi  + \\alpha }\\right) \\rbrack$ .\n\n## 练习 9.4(1)\n\n1. 下列复数是否用三角形式来表示的? 为什么?\n\n(1)3π(cos 0.5+i sin 0.5)； (2) $2\\left( {\\sin 1 + \\mathrm{i}\\cos 1}\\right)$ ；\n\n(3) $\\cos {131\\pi } + \\mathrm{i}\\sin {131\\pi }$ ； (4) $\\sqrt{2}\\left( {\\cos {0.3\\pi } + \\mathrm{i}\\sin {0.2\\pi }}\\right)$ ；\n\n(5) $- 2\\left( {\\cos \\frac{\\pi }{4} + \\mathrm{i}\\sin \\frac{\\pi }{4}}\\right)$ ； (6) $3\\left( {\\cos \\frac{\\pi }{5} - \\mathrm{i}\\sin \\frac{\\pi }{5}}\\right)$ .\n\n2. 把下列复数用三角形式表示(用辐角主值):\n\n(1) 3; (2)-2i;\n\n(3) $1 + \\mathrm{i}$ ； (4)-1+ $\\sqrt{3}\\mathrm{i}$ .\n\n## 2 三角形式下复数的乘除运算\n\n现在我们讨论三角形式下的复数乘除运算公式.\n\n设有两个用三角形式表示的复数 ${z}_{1} = r\\left( {\\cos \\alpha  + \\mathrm{i}\\sin \\alpha }\\right)$ 与 ${z}_{2} = s\\left( {\\cos \\beta  + \\mathrm{i}\\sin \\beta }\\right)$ ,其中 $r = \\left| {z}_{1}\\right|  \\geq  0, s = \\left| {z}_{2}\\right|  \\geq  0$ ,则\n\nQ\n\n$$\n{z}_{1}{z}_{2} = {rs}\\left\\lbrack  {\\cos \\left( {\\alpha  + \\beta }\\right)  + \\mathrm{i}\\sin \\left( {\\alpha  + \\beta }\\right) }\\right\\rbrack  ;\n$$\n\n$$\n\\frac{{z}_{1}}{{z}_{2}} = \\frac{r}{s}\\left\\lbrack  {\\cos \\left( {\\alpha  - \\beta }\\right)  + \\mathrm{i}\\sin \\left( {\\alpha  - \\beta }\\right) }\\right\\rbrack  \\left( {{z}_{2} \\neq  0}\\right) .\n$$\n\n---\n\n三角形式下的复数乘除运算公式称为棣莫弗公式.\n\n---\n\n![bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_23_251_1624_193_214_0.jpg","target":"images/bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_23_251_1624_193_214_0.jpg","line":969},{"title":"bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_25_579_402_887_307_0.jpg","target":"images/bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_25_579_402_887_307_0.jpg","line":1091,"embedded":true},{"title":"bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_25_221_1468_255_315_0.jpg","target":"images/bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_25_221_1468_255_315_0.jpg","line":1117,"embedded":true}],"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[],"last_embed":{"hash":"faettw","at":1773193875792}},"smart_blocks:精品资料-md 版本/上海教材md/必修二第9章复数/必修二第9章复数-dollar.md###9.1 复数及其四则运算": {"path":null,"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.084622,0.00849833,-0.00991087,-0.02444602,0.0155349,-0.01434891,-0.04640601,-0.02788453,0.03923751,-0.0146996,0.02843448,-0.06388108,0.0821514,0.02006661,-0.00195103,-0.00827159,-0.03345024,-0.0641879,-0.04437367,0.02455565,0.06425286,-0.06707434,0.02291539,-0.04893896,0.04115586,0.00961839,0.02632057,-0.02143336,0.01597423,-0.17623766,-0.00148063,0.01794817,-0.01531305,0.02352121,0.04262983,-0.01084148,-0.05227767,0.02375541,-0.00316887,0.04489551,-0.00918311,0.04705802,0.03346479,-0.01488788,0.03912375,-0.0587402,0.05699272,-0.01247595,0.05386716,-0.03130956,-0.00689108,-0.01774383,-0.01689261,0.04172125,0.03272643,0.01285697,0.03504752,0.07230054,-0.00704441,0.00875115,0.05409161,0.05731687,-0.23633002,0.05176818,0.03679321,-0.02381001,-0.0053775,0.03881485,0.02253849,0.06319146,-0.05470449,-0.02045419,0.00095325,0.02764379,-0.02725429,-0.05682956,0.02499317,-0.07299457,-0.01884403,-0.02112817,0.00787139,0.07946854,0.0078